## Push Karne Se Pehle Confirm Karo

`.env` file mein yeh hain — yeh **kabhi** GitHub pe nahi jaane chahiye:
```
RELAYER_PRIVATE_KEY=0x...   ← Private key leak = tokens chori
VEC_TOKEN_ADDRESS=0x...
RPC_URL=...